@startuml US_2.2.2_SSD
autonumber

actor "Port Authority\nOfficer" as Officer
participant ":System" as System

== Register Vessel ==
activate Officer
Officer -> System: Clica na secção "Vessel"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta página com lista de vessels registados e opção "Register Vessel"
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Register Vessel"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de registo de vessel
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Introduz dados do vessel(vesselName, vesselTypeId, operator, capacity, rows, bays, tiers, length) e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Update Vessel ==
Officer -> System: Seleciona vessel da lista
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta detalhes do vessel
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Edit Vessel"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de edição preenchido
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Modifica dados do vessel e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Search Vessels ==
Officer -> System: Introduz critérios de pesquisa (IMO, name, operator)
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta lista de vessels filtrados
deactivate System
deactivate Officer

@enduml
